    13вҶ’## Converting Tomli to tomllib вҖҰ
    15вҶ’### Sync status
    17вҶ’`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18вҶ’matches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19вҶ’
    20вҶ’### Steps to convert
    22вҶ’- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
    23вҶ’
    24вҶ’- Remove `__version__ = ...` line from `cpython:Lib/tomllib/__init__.py`
    25вҶ’
